'''巴什洛河'''（'''Bashilo River'''）是位於[[埃塞俄比亞|埃塞俄比亞]]的河流，發源自[[阿姆哈拉州|阿姆哈拉州]]，最後與[[青尼羅河|青尼羅河]]匯流，集水區13,242平方公里<ref>[http://www-wds.worldbank.org/external/default/WDSContentServer/WDSP/IB/2008/05/09/000334955_20080509032052/Rendered/PDF/434000PAD0P09617372B01off0use0only1.pdf "Tana & Beles Integrated Water Resources Development: Project Appraisal Document (PAD), Vol.1"] {{Wayback|url=http://www-wds.worldbank.org/external/default/WDSContentServer/WDSP/IB/2008/05/09/000334955_20080509032052/Rendered/PDF/434000PAD0P09617372B01off0use0only1.pdf |date=20160304193613 }}, World Bank, 2 May 2008 (accessed 5 May 2009)</ref>。巴什洛河曾被用作[[埃塞俄比亞|埃塞俄比亞]]州份的界線。

